      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in an exquisite state of preservation, maintaining its original showroom luster and mechanical integrity. Meticulously curated and presented in flawless condition, it represents a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing short of perfection. Experience the pinnacle of refined engineering and aesthetic excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
